# Blog Module Rules

## BlogPost Entity

Blog article on platform.

## BlogPost Fields

- `id` - Unique identifier
- `title` - Article title
- `description` - Short description
- `content` - Full article text
- `category` - Article category
- `author` - Author name
- `image` - Image URL
- `readTime` - Reading time (minutes)
- `published` - Whether article is published
- `createdAt` - Creation date
- `updatedAt` - Update date

## Blog Endpoints

- `GET /api/blog/posts` - Get list of published posts (with pagination)
- `GET /api/blog/posts/:id` - Get post details
- `POST /api/blog/posts` - Create post (admin only)
- `PATCH /api/blog/posts/:id` - Update post (admin only)
- `DELETE /api/blog/posts/:id` - Delete post (admin only)

## Blog Service

- Get published posts only for public
- Support pagination and filtering by category
- Calculate reading time based on content length
- Admin can create, update, and delete posts

## Business Logic

- Only published posts are visible to public
- Calculate read time: ~200 words per minute
- Support categories for filtering
- Sort by creation date (newest first)
